reviews.review: É bom, mas não funciona por si mesmo. Pensei que fosse ser um copilado de cenas empolgantes como The Last Jedi, mas não. Uma cena ou outra é empolgante, mas o foco é no desenvolvimento do Thanos - um dos vilões mais bem desenvolvidos de todos os tempos.
A excellent movie,much better than I thought

How is this movie 84%. I mean seriously. Amazing camera work, amazing sfx, computer generated image is almost imperceptible... The cast is amazing and the plot is huge. The villains are amazing and the main villain makes you wanna love him because it's purpose is not selfish, but want's salvation for the Universe in a wrong way. Thanos has feeliings like every human, heroes have feelings... It's a really complete movie. Such a she it has a lower rating than, for example, Black Panther... I guess it could have a better rating if Black Panther saved the day at the end, huh? Disgusting.
AWESOME!!! loved how all the Marvel characters came together.
i love the movie cryed a bunch and if you havent seen it yet i greatly recommend it!!!!

Once the first part of the movie settles (the most complicated part of the movie, both to process and to create), the action and emotion of the movie reach epic levels. If you're a comic book fan, you might know where this all thing is going, but the movie plays with the circumstances in a way, that the story is not that predictable and quite stimulating. And if you're not, well, you probably will get out of the theatre very surprised.
Ps: Thanos is a superb villain.
We've waited long enough and were not let down!
